org.yawlfoundation.yawl.worklet.admin

Class AdministrationTask

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.yawlfoundation.yawl.worklet.admin.AdministrationTask

  • public class AdministrationTask
extends java.lang.Object
    This class stores the details of a pending administration task, viewed via the worklet admin screens. The AdminTasksManager maintains a set of these AdministrationTask instances.
    Version:
    0.8, 04-09/2006
    Author:
    Michael Adams
